          <groundspeak:finder id="722399">thndrstrck</groundspeak:finder>
          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">I stink at puzzle cache solving. But I do like personal goals and challenges, so I have added this event to my calendar. Got to fill in another date on my Regular Event Calendar (REC), and maybe learn how to solve some of the puzzles in the area.</groundspeak:text>
        </groundspeak:log>
