          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">Thanks for the event

TFTC - Find number 838 Saturday February 28, 2026 10:57 AM ~cattrain from Kansas City</groundspeak:text>
        </groundspeak:log>
        <groundspeak:log id="1346716732">
          <groundspeak:date>2026-02-28T20:00:00Z</groundspeak:date>
          <groundspeak:type>Attended</groundspeak:type>
          <groundspeak:finder id="52918129">BellaTheHedgehog</groundspeak:finder>
          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">Attended with dad (cattrain) and grandma (cyndicow). Thanks for the event</groundspeak:text>
        </groundspeak:log>
        <groundspeak:log id="1346787123">
          <groundspeak:date>2026-02-28T20:00:00Z</groundspeak:date>
          <groundspeak:type>Attended</groundspeak:type>
          <groundspeak:finder id="2324839">MeToo1865</groundspeak:finder>
          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">When I got up today, I decided to take a drive to Omaha to attend this event.  I had not met kilroy18 and there were a few geocaches in the area of the event.  Seemed like a good day.

It was a small group a the event.  It was interesting comparing notes of experiences with those in attendance.  I will need to consider attending another event at this location in the future.</groundspeak:text>
        </groundspeak:log>
        <groundspeak:log id="1346705116">
          <groundspeak:date>2026-02-28T18:15:29Z</groundspeak:date>
          <groundspeak:type>Attended</groundspeak:type>
          <groundspeak:finder id="15777154">kilroy18</groundspeak:finder>
          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">A nice turnout.  Thanks for coming. </groundspeak:text>
        </groundspeak:log>
        <groundspeak:log id="1346819740">
          <groundspeak:date>2026-02-28T17:15:00Z</groundspeak:date>
          <groundspeak:type>Attended</groundspeak:type>
          <groundspeak:finder id="780848">cyndicow</groundspeak:finder>
          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">Thanks for the great conversation 😀 
 It was great to meet you both. </groundspeak:text>
        </groundspeak:log>
      </groundspeak:logs>
    </groundspeak:cache>
  </wpt>
