      <groundspeak:short_description html="True">&lt;b&gt;19 February 2026, 11:30 - 12:30&lt;/b&gt;</groundspeak:short_description>
      <groundspeak:long_description html="True">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:&amp;amp;quot;"&gt;Come on for some nice barbecue at Oklahoma Joe’s in Aksarben Village before the holiday.  All you need to do is show up and “hi.”  The street address is 1912 S 67th St, Omaha, NE 68106.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
